        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Ghoul spellcasters use these smaller cousins to skavelings as familiars. An evil spellcaster can gain a sootwing bat as a familiar at 5th level by taking the Improved Familiar feat. A sootwing bat familiar grants its master a +1 bonus to channel resistance (if the master has any)."
